1
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,120
You must be an angel.

2
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:51,560
You look just like someone I know.

3
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,160
You're giving me that speech again.

4
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:55,720
What?

5
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:59,060
Haven't you had enough of your role-playing games?

6
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,920
Keep your voice down.

7
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:03,050
Let's talk when we're somewhere safe.

8
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,440
Okay.

9
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:16,720
Go.

10
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:24,760
Hurry.

11
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,720
(Thai) Where are the people in the room?

12
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,320
Hello.

13
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:04,960
I'm sorry. We've done our best.

14
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,400
Thank you.

15
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:13,800
How is she?

16
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,640
She is terminally ill.

17
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,570
There is no cure.

18
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,380
Your mother...

19
00:03:26,079 --> 00:03:27,340
AI Xiaofei's analysis

20
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,760
found traces of another AI

21
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,840
inside her.

22
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,640
If I'm not mistaken,

23
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,240
this is the Princess personality

24
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,700
born in the virtual space.

25
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,000
A real princess

26
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:39,040
who keeps recovering her memories.

27
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,980
This must be Black Snake's doing.

28
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,600
He used his own people

29
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:45,770
to implant another dark personality.

30
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,760
They are constantly searching for Buluotuo's Tears.

31
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:49,280
If Black Snake succeeds,

32
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,000
Aya

33
00:03:53,079 --> 00:03:56,140
will be completely replaced by the other personality.

34
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,840
No.

35
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,180
I must save her.

36
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,680
I'll use Buluotuo's Tear.

37
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,360
I want to hear her

38
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,960
explain everything myself.

39
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,560
Buluotuo's Tear is an artifact.

40
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,200
If you use it

41
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,760
for your own selfish desires,

42
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:08,240
how are you different from Black Snake?

43
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,960
If it stays buried underground

44
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,120
or sits in a museum,

45
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,560
that would be a waste of a treasure.

46
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,880
Technology is so advanced nowadays.

47
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:16,120
If Buluotuo's Tears really is a cure-all,

48
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:18,120
we can definitely crack its formula

49
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,820
and benefit everyone.

50
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:37,100
Godfather,

51
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:38,480
Aya's signal is gone.

52
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,200
We have to save Aya.

53
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,640
Even if you find her,

54
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,400
so what?

55
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,360
Deep down,

56
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,580
she never cared about you.

57
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,040
Besides,

58
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:52,400
we can't find her now.

59
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,320
Where are you going?

60
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:01,760
She was deceived.

61
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,300
I want revenge.

62
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:09,960
You're a fool.

63
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:13,080
You still don't get it.

64
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,720
The current Aya has been reborn.

65
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,240
Reborn?

66
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:23,600
Luckily, I transplanted the AI-awakened

67
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,170
princess consciousness into her.

68
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:29,560
Isn't that the perfect rebirth for Aya?

69
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,920
You harmed her.

70
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:34,720
I'm helping her

71
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,640
achieve her dreams.

72
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:43,960
Whether it's Yuwen Ying or Aya,

73
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,480
once you're done using them,

74
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,740
you just discard them.

75
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,760
Now it's my turn.

76
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,159
I'll find a way to bring Aya back.

77
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,520
Aya won't die.

78
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:05,810
Boss, I found the coordinates for the virtual space.

79
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,720
In three minutes,

80
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,160
if I don't make it out,

81
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,320
you must activate

82
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,780
the protection protocol.

83
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,280
That's my limit.

84
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,520
Princess.
